--INPUT
fun(foo, *bar)
--LOCATIONS
   ~ begin ()
             ~ end ()
~~~ selector ()
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ expression ()
    ~~~ name (args[0])
    ~~~ expression (args[0])
         ~ operator (args[1])
         ~~~~ expression (args[1])
          ~~~ name (args[1]/value)
          ~~~ expression (args[1]/value)
--AST
